schlichen Daseins oder Finanzanlageobjekt - und verweist auf die Vorstellungen von Raum und Raumordnungen, die diesen Aushandlungsprozessen zugrunde liegen.  aThis volume shows how land is currently being renegotiated as a collective commodity, private property, fertile soil for human existence, or as an object of financial investment by identifying the ideas of space and spatial order on which these processes of negotiation are based.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aAgri-Food-System. 4aKlimawandel. 4aLand. 4aRaumpolitik. 7aHISTORY / Modern / General.2bisacsh  aAgri-Food-System.  aClimate change.  aCountry.  aSpatial policy.1 aBöhme, Michaela, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021z9783110753851oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831106416460 cprintz978311064141740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110645583zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110645583zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110645583/original  a978-3-11-075070-6 DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-GOA